{"tid":253631,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] playerunknown's battlegrounds (2)","createTime":"2017-05-22T14:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T12:25:06.000Z","uid":384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26570dcaf67ed3b0a53408c96a06aa702b74f780","tid":253631,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"無人開我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242d0486ffc0ed55498874b00b504a6615fde948","tid":253631,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人開tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e4c1e0f2bd8a2108a6889ded613c1d3e0281eb","tid":253631,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人開tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打tg係咩 我加你開左先"},{"pid":"23854af5654741e422c9404a2a7a0d1567745e31","tid":253631,"uid":62068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"又成功雙排食雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd836434fc270d108cb1514b52e11debfa6916ee","tid":253631,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人開tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打tg係咩 我加你開左先</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kyhryan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkyhryan&d=gxWz%2FC6C71p60fUhkgd6dC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3d261d83\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kyhryan</a>"},{"pid":"c8b359dbbe6